name: gss_OID_set_desc_struct
desc: The structure for an OID set descriptor that manages an array of OID descriptors.

items.name: var count: Int
items.desc: The number of OID descriptors in the array.

items.name: var elements: gss_OID!
items.desc: A pointer to the array of OID descriptors.

items.name: init()
items.desc: Initialize a new, empty object identifier set.

items.name: init(count: Int, elements: gss_OID!)
items.desc: Initialize a new object identifier set with the given identifiers.
